<p>The <b>Associação Brasileira dos Produtores de Discos</b> (<b>ABPD</b>) (<a href="English_language" title="English language">English</a>: Brazilian Association of Record Producers) is an official representative body of the record labels in the Brazilian phonographic market.<sup id="cite_ref-ABPD-About_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-ABPD-About-1"><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<table id="toc" class="toc">
<tr>
