<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Associa%C3%A7%C3%A3o_Brasileira_dos_Produtores_de_Discos&action=edit&section=3.php.html" title="Edit section: Sales certification">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Sales_certification">Sales certification</span></h2>
<p>Before 1990, there are no music certification award, in Brazil. Following that, the certification levels were:<sup id="cite_ref-5" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-5"><span>[</span>5<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
